    "title": "How to assert an exception is thrown with JUnit 5?",
    "body": "<p>Is there a better way to assert that a method throws an exception in JUnit 5?</p>\n<p>Currently, I have to use a <code>@Rule</code> in order to verify that my test throws an exception, but this doesn't work for the cases where I expect multiple methods to throw exceptions in my test.</p>\n"
